<section class="slide-regimes">
  <h2>Regimes</h2>
    <h3>Zero field</h3>
    <p>
      $$
      \Delta R_{\text{NL}} = \left( P_{\Sigma}^L \right)^2 R_N e^{- L / \lambda}
      $$
    </p>
    <h3>Tunneling contacts</h3>
    <p>
      $$
      f^{\infty}
      = \text{Re}
        {\frac{e^{- \left( L / \lambda \right) \sqrt{1 + i \omega \tau}}}
        {2 \sqrt{1 + i \omega \tau}}}
      $$
    </p>
  <h3>Fits independent of lifetime</h3>
  <p>\( \lambda / r \gg \sqrt{\omega \tau} \gg 1 \)</p>
  <p>
    Zeros determined by
    $$
    L \sqrt{\frac{D}{2 \omega}} + \frac{\pi}{4} = \frac{n \pi}{2}
    $$
  </p>
